$interpreted: Officer: King Theodore, the other squads have been driven back one after the other. We can't hold on much longer!
Theodore: ......
Angelia: Theodore, you are on the verge of defeat. Surrender!
Theodore: Surrender...?
Theodore: ...A naive little girl like you doesn't have the right to speak to me like that!
Theodore: Listen up, men! Offer your lives to Kingdom of the Sun and rid this land of the traitors! For those who attempt to run...I shall show no mercy!
Naya: It's over...
Theodore: ......
Kittyeyes: Brother!
Roger: Don't come over! This guy is seriously bad news!
Angelia: Sir Dagger!? What is happening?
Dagger: That's my question! Just what in world is that "thing"!? Is that even human!?
Angelia: What?
Ralph: ...Found you...
Theodore: This voice...are you...Ralph?
Naya: He's giving off a really strong scent of blood...!
Dagger: On his way here, he's been sucking blood nonstop.
Ralph: His Majesty Theodore's enemies...
Dagger: Here he comes! Angelia, be careful!
Ralph: Your...Majesty...please...go...your loyal servant...has done...his best...
Theodore: ......
Theodore: ...Worthless fool! Who cares if you did you best if you didn't succeed?
Ralph: ......
Theodore: And look at yourself now; an ugly mess. I shouldn't have used you in the first place.
Theodore: Answer me, Ralph! Is this the best you can do?
Kittyeyes: HEY! He is trying to help you! Why are you so harsh to──
Ralph: No...no...
Ralph: No, No, No, NOOOOOOO! I...I can do so much more!!
Theodore: Then prove it to me! Become my final line of defense, Ralph Lavande!
Ralph: I'm not a worthless fool...NOT WORTHLESS!!!
Ralph: ARRGGGHHHHH!!
Dagger: Where's Theodore！?
Naya: Is he trying to seize Rayzor's core!?
Theodore: As long as I take this thing back to the capitol, there's nothing else you can do!
Theodore: Soldiers, escort me out of here!
